# Code index — always refresh after exports

When you add, change, or remove **exported** symbols in `apps/web-react` or `apps/api`:

1. Run: `python scripts/code_index_refresh.py --repo .` (must exit 0)
2. If validate fails with `missing human purpose`, add `purpose` in the correct `docs/context/*.md` file — see [CODE-INDEX.md](docs/context/CODE-INDEX.md)
3. Confirm: `python scripts/code_index_query.py --repo . missing_tests` returns `[]`

**UI rules:** no hex/rgb outside `apps/web-react/src/styles/theme.css`; no user-facing string literals in JSX — use react-i18next + `docs/context/fe-i18n.md`.

**Bug-fix tasks:** debugger must write `docs/working/<TASK-ID>/test-gap.md`; testing agent implements every listed regression test.
